An elementary school needs a system to calculate grades, but depending on the grade, the subjects vary and that generates a more complex job to be able to calculate the average of each student correctly.

The director wants the teachers to be able to enter the name of the student they are going to evaluate, then how many subjects they are going to grade, then, enter each grade. If the result is greater than 6, it should show a message that he/she passed, if it is less, it should show a message that he/she needs to be retaken and if the grade is equal to 10, it should show a message that he/she is an outstanding student.

At the end, the program should show a report with the name of the student, his/her final average and the message that will depend on his/her grade. For delivery, attach the code in a text file (. txt)


Algoritmo sin_titulo
	Escribir "El nombre del alumno"
	Leer alumno
	Escribir "Materias a calificar"
	Leer macali
    Para i <- 1 Hasta macali Hacer
        Escribir "ingresa calificacion ", i, ": "
        Leer cali
		sumar = sumar + cali
	FinPara
	
	promedio = sumar / macali
	
	si promedio > 6 Entonces
		mj = "La calificacion es aprobatorio"
	SiNo
		mj= "La calificacion es reprobatorio "
	FinSi
	si promedio = 10 Entonces
		mj= "Es alumno destacado"
	FinSi
	Escribir "El alumno", alumno, "Tiene promedio de: ", promedio," ", mj
FinAlgoritmo

*** Ejecución Iniciada. ***
El nombre del alumno
> meli
Materias a calificar
> 4
ingresa calificacion 1:
> 10
ingresa calificacion 2:
> 10
ingresa calificacion 3:
> 10
ingresa calificacion 4:
> 10
El alumnomeliTiene promedio de: 10 Es alumno destacado
